PrecisTransfer to the Province of BRITISH COLUMBIA, for the purpose of establishing an ecological reserve, of the administration and control of all Crown interests in some 35 acres of land known as the "TRIAL ISLANDS" situated across from McNeil Bay in the Juan de Fuca Strait, with the exception of a parcel required by the Department of Transport for the purposes of a lighthouse.
